&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Active LSW or LPC in Illinois &lt;em&gt;(required — we are not able to hire pre-licensure candidates at this time)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Bilingual Spanish/English fluency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Experience or strong interest in working with school-aged youth and families&lt;/li&gt;
